ii - BEACH added
- BONE added
(1 Mark per -, Max 2)2 (AO2.1)
Whether branches point left or right or
order of branches is irrelevant. As long as
branches form the words without
unnecessary repetition of nodes, award the
marks.
Examiner’s Comments
Invariably, all candidates fared well on both
parts of this question.
